Novem(bres) occurs repeatedly. On Anavis, Caecilia see Introd. 32. On the eidus interkalares see note on Terminalia, n. 109. Licnia = Licinia. Protarcus (132) (i.e. τάμε) is a state-slave (publicus servos). Tei-(etms) (133), sc. tribu. (Not Terente'na.) The form ossiva (= ossa) is strange.
